<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Order Management</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body class="bg-slate-100 text-slate-800">
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl p-6">
        <header class="mb-6">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-indigo-700">Order Collection</h1>
            <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Total orders: <%= orders.length %> · Total amount: <strong>
                        <%= totalAmountFromDB %>
                    </strong></p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600">Count product_id = "somi": <strong>
                    <%= productCount %>
                </strong></p>
        </header>

        <section class="rounded-lg bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <h2 class="mb-4 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-700">Product Summary</h2>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
                <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-slate-200 text-sm">
                    <thead class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">
                        <tr>
                            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">No</th>
                            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Order ID</th>
                            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Product name</th>
                            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Price</th>
                            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Quantity</th>
                            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Total</th>
                            <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Delivery address</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100 bg-white">
                        <% tableRows.forEach((row, idx)=> { %>
                            <tr class="hover:bg-slate-50">
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">
                                    <%= idx + 1 %>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">
                                    <%= row.orderid %>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">
                                    <%= row.product_name %>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">
                                    <%= row.price.toFixed(2) %>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">
                                    <%= row.quantity %>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">
                                    <%= row.total.toFixed(2) %>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3">
                                    <%= row.delivery_address %>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <% }); %>
                    </tbody>
                    <tfoot class="bg-slate-50 font-semibold">
                        <tr>
                            <td class="px-4 py-3" colspan="5">Total Grand</td>
                            <td class="px-4 py-3">
                                <%= totalAmountFromDB.toFixed(2) %>
                            </td>
                            <td class="px-4 py-3"></td>
                        </tr>
                    </tfoot>
                </table>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mt-5 rounded-lg bg-white p-4 shadow-sm">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-700">Action Examples</h2>
            <ol class="mt-2 list-decimal pl-4 text-sm text-slate-600">
                <li>Gửi POST /orders/batch với JSON array để insert nhiều document.</li>
                <li>Gửi PATCH /orders/{orderid}/delivery-address với body { "delivery_address": "New Hanoi" }.</li>
                <li>Gửi DELETE /orders/{_id} để xoá order theo _id.</li>
                <li>Gửi GET /orders/view để xem bảng và tổng.</li>
            </ol>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>

</html>